Founder of Christ Mercyland Church, in Warri, Delta State, Prophet Jeremiah Fufeyin, has donated some money to veteran Nollywood actor, Michael Duru, who has been battling with an amputated leg due to his diabetes condition. The actor, who has been confined to his hometown, had in a viral video begged Nigerians to assist him as he could not afford an artificial leg that he estimated at about N600,000. According to reports, the attention of the billionaire prophet was drawn to the video and thereafter he sent a delegation to Duruâ€™s home in Anambra to present a cash gift of N5 million to him with the aim of alleviating his pains.